description:
A Buff Clan soldier under the jurisdiction of Harulu, she accompanies Hannibal Gen to Rukuku Kil`s Garowa Zan in order to spy on her.

Kulara assassinates Rukuku under Harulu`s orders in order to get a video with Daram on it, and as revenge for Rukuku laughing at it. Her effort is worthless however as the entire ship is blown up soon after.
name: Kulara Kina
